{"tid":1063940,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣後悔係外國讀書冇溝鬼妹","createTime":"2019-03-16T07:11:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T16:08:26.000Z","uid":57378,"like":1,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3bb60bb65d75dc6a040af6fc2275d7eca2dc6846","tid":1063940,"uid":57378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T07:11:02.000Z","msg":"簡單介紹下我個背景先<br />\n本人178<br />\n亞洲人角度黎睇我個樣應該都有75-80分<br />\n體重63kg身型都算係健碩唔係太大隻又唔係太瘦<br />\n家底算係有錢出街食飯唔會就住就住<br />\n個人談吐正常喺外國嗰班香港朋友圈子入邊我都可以叫做萬人迷<br />\n<br />\n入正題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我本身由細到大都幾鍾意鬼妹<br />\n我鍾意鬼妹除咗貪佢哋樣靚身材正之外仲覺得佢哋好開朗talkative同埋性方面好open<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢幾點到深深吸引住我<br />\n成日睇YouTube啲片見到啲靚嘅鬼妹就成日喺度諗如果佢係我女朋友就好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PJPXiND.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPJPXiND.png&h=e089dd83&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/psez5sF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpsez5sF.png&h=c10873a0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PAcYNF3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPAcYNF3.png&h=15b57b2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（鬼妹示意圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n嗰陣時我仲喺度諗到時去到外國一定要溝番個鬼妹<br />\n溝唔到至少都同佢哋打個車輪還返個心願<br />\n<br />\n點知都我有機會去外國讀書我都冇把握到任何嘅機會去溝鬼妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有幾次我啲香港朋友叫埋我一齊去night club嗰度Yo女我都推咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原因無他都係因為我有少少怕羞同埋驚到時同啲鬼妹溝通唔到就奶西（雖然我雅思speaking 都有7.5） <br />\n<br />\n又有一次我groupmate上上下堂突然問我地個group啲人有冇興趣去佢返工嗰間disco 嗰度玩which is 應該係全悉尼最出名嘅disco 黎<br />\n點知最後我啲鬼佬組員同我都冇去到（我估大家都唔夠膽去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n學校上堂嗰啲鬼妹同學全部都係hi bye friend甚至溝通都冇溝通過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n眼見班臭雞港女日日都去club 都溝鬼佬都真係幾葡萄佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家真係好後悔點解我冇溝過鬼妹連親密接觸都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人明我感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f456f4e116e94095a08f1578d9537826109eaf9","tid":1063940,"uid":69083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T07:21:37.000Z","msg":"無是咁的 重作 0分"},{"pid":"3f5a2bdc9c94fae5057cc02ec676d18cc0450275","tid":1063940,"uid":240107,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T07:24:59.000Z","msg":"你都識講亞洲人角度<br />\n可能佢地睇你覺得你好樣衰呢"},{"pid":"858d9038e137fa56cf5bdd00c4f0fc5f03b1a8bf","tid":1063940,"uid":241930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f5a2bdc9c94fae5057cc02ec676d18cc0450275","tid":1063940,"uid":240107,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T07:24:59.000Z","msg":"你都識講亞洲人角度<br />\n可能佢地睇你覺得你好樣衰呢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T07:29:12.000Z","msg":"正解 (雖然係其次).<br />\n<br />\n你係social嘅話其實係加勁多分. 英文好嘅就更好.<br />\n<br />\n樓主幾耐之前喺邊度讀? 讀幾耐?"},{"pid":"8a70968540a066402f34c30d88d445349f9cb946","tid":1063940,"uid":111256,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T07:29:23.000Z","msg":"算啦 溝都未必溝到"},{"pid":"9d244bb2f879a2ff46c480b5063cecc7a6d41410","tid":1063940,"uid":66521,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T07:29:44.000Z","msg":"後悔有咩用, 想做又唔敢做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e18024e34ab8908f8e23a0d60e69bcb40dcd2fb3","tid":1063940,"uid":189163,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T07:31:11.000Z","msg":"得把口唔敢做收撚皮啦<br />\n<br />\n話自己中上樣，自貼上嚟囉"},{"pid":"35f1fb647e1977b12c8cecfa78d201763e047fdd","tid":1063940,"uid":57378,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"3f5a